			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="talk">
			<div class="date">June 2024</div>
			<div>
				<h3>Computing the Mertens Function</h3>
				<p>Bachelor's thesis defense, Université Paris Cité — <a href="/mertens/diapo_mertens.pdf">Slides</a></p>
			</div>
